--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
CHANGES
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        o
    ____|____
   |         |  This file lists changes made to the Ansible role.
   |  _   _  |  The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and
   | [_] [_] |  formatted to allow easy grepping by scripts.
   |____~____|
    ___//__//   The fields are:
   /|     |/    B: bug
  //|_____|     F: feature
    _|| ||_     I: improvement
   (__| |__)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 0.5.0 (2014-08-25)
F: Add support for OS family 'FreeBSD'

* Version 0.4.0 (2014-08-14)
F: Remove support for OS family 'RedHat'

* Version 0.3.2 (2014-08-14)
I: Improve conditional statements

* Version 0.3.1 (2014-07-22)
I: Improve SSH client options to prevent SSH MITM (Downgrade) Attack

* Version 0.3.0 (2014-07-07)
F: Add support for 'UseDNS' option

* Version 0.2.3 (2014-05-26)
B: Fix issue with 'openssh_print_motd' (PrintMotd) option

* Version 0.2.2 (2014-05-26)
B: Move file configuration from 'install' to 'enable' task

* Version 0.2.1 (2014-05-26)
I: Change default value of 'openssh_print_motd' (PrintMotd) option

* Version 0.2.0 (2014-05-05)
F: Add support for running OpenSSH on multiple ports

* Version 0.1.0 (2014-04-28)
F: Initial release
